snippet.title: RowBot Rally - Playdate Update Showcase
snippet.description:
🛶 A re-upload of my segment in the 5th Playdate Update. https://youtu.be/1I9mO4pYBPI
❤️ Wishlist RowBot Rally on Catalog TODAY!: https://play.date/games/rowbot-rally

🐇 Thank you to Voxy for helping me edit this together! https://voxy.space
💛 ...and thank you to everyone at Panic for having me on! It's an absolute dream, really.

👋 This video's got a little about rae (that's me, hi), and a brief overview of what RowBot Rally is all about. If you want to hear a bit more about the process behind the video (among a lot of other things), you can read the dev log post on it here: https://stuffbyrae.itch.io/rowbot-rally/devlog/667615/playdate-update-showcase-more
